# PCI Glass — where things live

| Path | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `index.html` | Page markup & SEO |
| `style.css` | CSS entry (`@import`s only) |
| `css/tokens.css` | Palette, spacing, gradients |
| `css/themes.css` | **Theme colors** — edit `--t-*` vars for dark/light |
| `css/base.css` | Reset, grain, theme transition |
| `css/components.css` | Layout & components (uses `var(--t-*)`) |
| `css/responsive.css` | Breakpoints & reduced motion |
| `js/site.js` | All frontend behavior (theme, nav, hero, gallery, form) |
| `server.js` | Express app, static files, `/api/quote` |
| `lib/email.js` | Quote email HTML templates |

**Theme changes:** `css/themes.css` only.

**Frontend behavior:** `js/site.js` only.

**Ignore:** `node_modules/`
